com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class StateSet<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.DoubleBufferSet<K,State<K>>
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.StateSet<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type parameter

    public class StateSet<K>
extends DoubleBufferSet<K,State<K>>
    A collection of State objects being staged for particular layers. Provides indexing capabilities to reference the deltas based on physical references (to double[] objects) and based on logical referants (i.e. layers) Provides collection-arithmetic operations appropriate to the State's 'point' geometric archtype.
